text: Ramon J. Alexander (born October 19, 1984) is a Democratic member of the Florida House of Representatives. He has represented the 8th District, which includes Gadsden County and sections of Tallahassee in Leon County, since 2016. Archived December 23, 2016. He graduated from Florida A&M; University with a Bachelor of Science degree in 2007.
